198564,"uid":209191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:02:31.000Z","msg":"好多宜加嘅30-40都係同一個心態：咪阻住搵食啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都係反映到當年社會民智未開嘅情況，捱慣窮變到淨係識搵錢；冇試過進行反對，變到政府講乜就乜。其實作為年輕人唔係想得到支持，而係純粹唔想佢地阻止，唔想聽到佢地前一句搞事後一句暴亂"},{"pid":"f99c9457c44a45ea0eca5693cba0bfe69de07778","tid":1198564,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"一早已經冇理屋企人<br />\n我全族都係賣港賊以前成日嘈<br />\n過左雨革之後已經廢撚事同佢地嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4cd93893fca99294ea68bb3412875e714c21d5","tid":1198564,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"所以改為恰鳩冇得反駁嘅爆機達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df078318569058727e84e2233fb0e4eac41fc0d8","tid":1198564,"uid":174199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:15:25.000Z","msg":"解釋左幾多次泛民出賣香港都仲係要追佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係迫我用行動"}]}